replies.body:
> If somebody is a Silver 1 Nasus OTP D-flasher and suddenly climbs to Plat 1 playing Ezreal and Twitch as an F-flasher with an 88% win rate, they're boosted,

tbh i used to use {{summoner:4}}  on different buttons back in the day, in the sense that i would attribute a higher priority to the use of D over F so depending on what summoners i had selected, {{summoner:4}}  could very well be closer to "A", priority wise. For example {{champion:37}} {{summoner:3}} {{summoner:4}}  and {{champion:98}}  {{summoner:4}} {{summoner:12}}

my point is that there can be valid exceptions to that "{{summoner:4}}  changed places therefore account shareing " theory
